        <source>isPreNote(): Boolean;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
10 November 2022	navkc1	Initial creation Bug 55382: MTN - Cargo Group Details recalculated after each change to TI when bulk editing

*/

vars

